{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2024-01-03","name":"Pierre Rogier de Beaufort","nameForms":[{"lang":"und","fullText":"Pierre Rogier de Beaufort","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Pierre"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"Rogier de Beaufort"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"alternateName":"Seigneur Pierre de Rogier de Beaufort","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1241–1300","fullLifespan":"environ 1241–1300","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/2jv3l/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7701-126597-9431-40/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/177536603","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7701-126597-9431-40/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-7701-126597-9431-40/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","headline":"Rogier de Beaufort D'argent à la bande d'azur accompagnée de six roses de gueules, trois en chef et trois en pointe.","description":"Armoirie de la famille Rogier de Beaufort : \nD'argent à la bande d'azur accompagnée de six roses de gueules, trois en chef et trois en pointe.","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1241","birthPlace":{"address":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","geo":{"latitude":45.3771,"longitude":2.0075,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"deathDate":"+1300","deathPlace":{"address":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","geo":{"latitude":45.3771,"longitude":2.0075,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"userCertifiedLifeSummary":"En tout cas les Roger ou Rogiers (de Rosiers certainement) étaient gros paysans ou petits seigneurs, très éventuellement de fraîche date, et bien peu visibles avant la 1ère moitié du XIIIème siècle. C'est le grand-père, Pierre Rogier, né vers 1240, qui lance réellement une belle famille qui va largement prospèrer. Il a au moins un fils, Guillem ou Guillaume, né vers 1265 et décédé en 1338  qui est marié avec Guillemette de La Monstre. L'ascension est spectaculaire autant que très mystérieuse.\nrelevé JPR Teyssier Chalancon Mangas","events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1241","date":"environ 1241","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France"},{"name":"Marriage","sources":"0","year":"1263","date":"1263","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Ussel, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","type":"Spousal","age":"22","id":"L2SP-QQ4"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1264","date":"1264","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","age":"23","id":"G2DH-TNQ"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1265","date":"1265","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","age":"24","id":"G22L-51Y"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1265","date":"8 janvier 1265","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","age":"24","id":"GMNF-36F"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1272","date":"1272","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","age":"31","id":"G2DH-5B7"},{"name":"Death","sources":"0","year":"1300","date":"1300","place":"Rosiers-d'Égletons, Corrèze, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","age":"59"}],"parent":[{"name":"Pierre Rogier de Beaufort","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1200–Male","birthDate":"/+1200","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/e0wdl/thumb64.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"@type":"Person","identifier":"G4RD-5KX","url":"https://ancestors.familysearch.org/en/G4RD-5KX/pierre-rogier-de-beaufort-1200","published":true}],"sibling":[{"name":"Pierre Rogier de Beaufort","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1241–1300","birthDate":"A+1241","deathDate":"+1300","age":59,"portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.fami